# Customer Config V2 API Testing
# ===============================
# This file contains HTTP requests for testing the Customer Config V2 API endpoints.
# 
# Prerequisites:
# 1. Install "REST Client" extension in Cursor/VS Code
# 2. Set your API key and organization ID below
# 3. Click "Send Request" above any request to execute
#
# Environment: Update these variables for your environment
# - local: http://localhost:3001
# - dev: https://spacecat-services--api-service.aem-dev.hlx.page
# - stage: https://spacecat-services--api-service.aem-stage.hlx.page
# - prod: https://spacecat-services--api-service.aem.hlx.page

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001
@apiKey = YOUR_API_KEY_HERE
@spaceCatId = dc6240fe-1c30-4f4f-a995-15aab11c100b

# =============================================================================
# CUSTOMER CONFIG - FULL
# =============================================================================

### Get full customer configuration (all brands, categories, topics, prompts)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v2/orgs/{{spaceCatId}}/llmo-customer-config
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

### Get full customer configuration - filter by active status
GET {{baseUrl}}/v2/orgs/{{spaceCatId}}/llmo-customer-config?status=active
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

### Get full customer configuration - include deleted items
GET {{baseUrl}}/v2/orgs/{{spaceCatId}}/llmo-customer-config?status=deleted
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

# =============================================================================
# CUSTOMER CONFIG - LEAN
# =============================================================================

### Get lean customer configuration (brands with counts, no prompts/categories/topics)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v2/orgs/{{spaceCatId}}/llmo-customer-config-lean
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

### Get lean customer configuration - filter by status
GET {{baseUrl}}/v2/orgs/{{spaceCatId}}/llmo-customer-config-lean?status=active
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

# =============================================================================
# TOPICS
# =============================================================================

### Get all topics
GET {{baseUrl}}/v2/orgs/{{spaceCatId}}/llmo-topics
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

### Get topics for Chevrolet brand
GET {{baseUrl}}/v2/orgs/{{spaceCatId}}/llmo-topics?brandId=chevrolet
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

### Get topics for GMC brand
GET {{baseUrl}}/v2/orgs/{{spaceCatId}}/llmo-topics?brandId=gmc
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

### Get topics for Buick brand
GET {{baseUrl}}/v2/orgs/{{spaceCatId}}/llmo-topics?brandId=buick
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

### Get topics for Cadillac brand
GET {{baseUrl}}/v2/orgs/{{spaceCatId}}/llmo-topics?brandId=cadillac
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

### Get topics for OnStar brand
GET {{baseUrl}}/v2/orgs/{{spaceCatId}}/llmo-topics?brandId=onstar
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

### Get topics for GM News brand
GET {{baseUrl}}/v2/orgs/{{spaceCatId}}/llmo-topics?brandId=gm-news
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

### Get only active topics
GET {{baseUrl}}/v2/orgs/{{spaceCatId}}/llmo-topics?status=active
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

### Get only deleted topics
GET {{baseUrl}}/v2/orgs/{{spaceCatId}}/llmo-topics?status=deleted
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

### Get active topics for a specific brand
GET {{baseUrl}}/v2/orgs/{{spaceCatId}}/llmo-topics?brandId=chevrolet&status=active
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

# =============================================================================
# PROMPTS
# =============================================================================

### Get all prompts (enriched with brand, category, topic info)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v2/orgs/{{spaceCatId}}/llmo-prompts
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

### Get prompts for Chevrolet brand
GET {{baseUrl}}/v2/orgs/{{spaceCatId}}/llmo-prompts?brandId=chevrolet
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

### Get prompts for GMC brand
GET {{baseUrl}}/v2/orgs/{{spaceCatId}}/llmo-prompts?brandId=gmc
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

### Get prompts for Buick brand
GET {{baseUrl}}/v2/orgs/{{spaceCatId}}/llmo-prompts?brandId=buick
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

### Get prompts for Cadillac brand
GET {{baseUrl}}/v2/orgs/{{spaceCatId}}/llmo-prompts?brandId=cadillac
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

### Get prompts for OnStar brand
GET {{baseUrl}}/v2/orgs/{{spaceCatId}}/llmo-prompts?brandId=onstar
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

### Get prompts for GM News brand
GET {{baseUrl}}/v2/orgs/{{spaceCatId}}/llmo-prompts?brandId=gm-news
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

### Get prompts by category
GET {{baseUrl}}/v2/orgs/{{spaceCatId}}/llmo-prompts?categoryId=product-features
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

### Get prompts by topic
GET {{baseUrl}}/v2/orgs/{{spaceCatId}}/llmo-prompts?topicId=performance
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

### Get active prompts only
GET {{baseUrl}}/v2/orgs/{{spaceCatId}}/llmo-prompts?status=active
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

### Get deleted prompts only
GET {{baseUrl}}/v2/orgs/{{spaceCatId}}/llmo-prompts?status=deleted
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

### Combine filters: Chevrolet active prompts
GET {{baseUrl}}/v2/orgs/{{spaceCatId}}/llmo-prompts?brandId=chevrolet&status=active
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

### Combine filters: Specific brand, category, and status
GET {{baseUrl}}/v2/orgs/{{spaceCatId}}/llmo-prompts?brandId=chevrolet&categoryId=product-features&status=active
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

# =============================================================================
# SAVE CUSTOMER CONFIG
# =============================================================================

### Save customer configuration to S3
POST {{baseUrl}}/v2/orgs/{{spaceCatId}}/llmo-customer-config
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

< ./../../scripts/v1v2test/generalmotors/757A02BE532B22BA0A490D4CAdobeOrg.json

# =============================================================================
# ERROR CASES (for testing error handling)
# =============================================================================

### Invalid organization ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/v2/orgs/invalid-uuid/llmo-customer-config
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

### Organization not found
GET {{baseUrl}}/v2/orgs/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/llmo-customer-config
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

### Missing API key (should return 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v2/orgs/{{spaceCatId}}/llmo-customer-config

### Invalid brand ID filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/v2/orgs/{{spaceCatId}}/llmo-prompts?brandId=non-existent-brand
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

### Invalid status filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/v2/orgs/{{spaceCatId}}/llmo-prompts?status=invalid-status
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

# =============================================================================
# WORKFLOW: Complete Test Scenario
# =============================================================================
# Run these in order to test a complete workflow:
#
# 1. Get lean config (overview of brands and counts)
# 2. Get all topics (see available topics)
# 3. Get topics for specific brand (filter by brand)
# 4. Get all prompts (see all prompts with enriched data)
# 5. Get prompts for specific brand (filter by brand)
# 6. Get prompts by category (filter by category)
# 7. Get prompts by topic (filter by topic)
# 8. Get full config (complete data with all prompts)
# 9. Save config (upload modified config to S3)
#
